*   Four-story high grand lobby of the [Paramount Theatre](/Paramount_Theatre_(Oakland,_California)) in [Oakland](/Oakland), California, by [Timothy Pflueger](/Timothy_Pflueger) (1932)
*   Auditorium and stage of [Radio City Music Hall](/Radio_City_Music_Hall) in New York City by [Edward Durell Stone](/Edward_Durell_Stone) and [Donald Deskey](/Donald_Deskey) (1932)
*   [Grand Rex](/Grand_Rex) in Paris by Auguste Bluysen, [John Eberson](/John_Eberson), Henri-Édouard Navarre and [Maurice Dufrêne](/Maurice_Dufr%C3%AAne) (1932)
*   The [Paramount](/Paramount_(Shanghai)) in [Shanghai](/Shanghai), China, by S. J. Young (1933)
